rmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0648\u064e\u0627\u062b\u0650\u0644\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0623\u064e\u0633\u0652\u0642\u064e\u0639\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2699,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/03\/31\/imam-care-people-needs\/","url_meta":{"origin":27142,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Imam: Muslim leaders must take care of people\u2019s needs","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 31, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"'Amr ibn Murrah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThere is no leader who closes the door to someone in need, in hardship, and\u00a0in poverty, but that Allah closes the gates of heaven to him when he is in need, in hardship, and\u00a0in poverty.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20829,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/08\/13\/dua-ease-answer-hardship\/","url_meta":{"origin":27142,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Supplicate in prosperity if you want answer in adversity","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 13, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever would like for Allah to answer him during times of hardship and difficulty, let him supplicate often during times of ease.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3382 Grade: Hasan (fair) accor